# Expected ADK oscdimg argument list, one argument per line, in order.
# This is tiny11builder's invocation (docs/PLAN.md section 2.2 step 13) with the volume label and
# boot images taken from the source ISO. oscdimg takes native Windows paths and derives the boot
# load sizes itself, so nothing here is /cygdrive and there is no -boot-load-size.
-m
-o
-u2
-udfver102
-lCCCOMA_X64FRE_EN-US_DV9
-bootdata:2#p0,e,bC:\scratch\iso\boot\etfsboot.com#pEF,e,bC:\scratch\iso\efi\microsoft\boot\efisys.bin
C:\scratch\iso
D:\out\tinywin.iso
